You saved my life over a decade ago.

595
00:30:55,720 --> 00:30:57,400
You were gored by a startled goat.

596
00:30:59,750 --> 00:31:00,550
Oh, I remember.

597
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:04,070
You were only this tall back then.

598
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:06,510
You're Principal Fang's daughter.

599
00:31:08,750 --> 00:31:09,880
I only just found out

600
00:31:10,270 --> 00:31:12,350
that Fang Jingyu was my foster mother.

601
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:14,680
My surname was supposed to be He.

602
00:31:21,550 --> 00:31:22,310
You won't admit it?

603
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:24,880
What do you want me to admit?

604
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:29,270
My sin?

605
00:31:39,160 --> 00:31:40,590
That's not what I mean.

606
00:31:41,920 --> 00:31:43,000
I just came to see...

607
00:31:44,790 --> 00:31:45,480
Where is she?

608
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:48,110
Who?

609
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:49,790
My mother.

610
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:52,270
She's dead.

611
00:31:53,440 --> 00:31:54,310
Long gone.

612
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:58,440
When you ditched me back then,

613
00:31:58,920 --> 00:31:59,680
my...

614
00:32:01,830 --> 00:32:03,350
Did she cry?

615
00:32:10,270 --> 00:32:12,640
It was sunny that day,

616
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:16,160
but suddenly,
there was thunder and rain.

617
00:32:19,110 --> 00:32:20,590
I didn't hear her crying.

618
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:26,350
But I think

619
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,440
she must have cried.

620
00:32:29,240 --> 00:32:31,110
She was pregnant with you for so long.

621
00:32:32,310 --> 00:32:33,270
It must have been tough.

622
00:32:34,880 --> 00:32:36,200
But she didn't even get to hold you.

623
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:38,880
How could she not be sad?

624
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,400
What about you?

625
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:45,030
Ditching me like that,

626
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:46,160
have you regretted it?

627
00:32:58,750 --> 00:32:59,510
I haven't.

628
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:02,880
I sent you to

629
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:05,160
a good family in town.

630
00:33:06,030 --> 00:33:07,590
That couple was old.

631
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:09,030
They were well-educated

632
00:33:09,510 --> 00:33:10,510
but had no children.

633
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:17,070
I thought it through carefully.

634
00:33:17,070 --> 00:33:18,440
It was the best choice for you.

635
00:33:19,510 --> 00:33:20,640
When I came back,

636
00:33:21,030 --> 00:33:22,200
someone even asked me

637
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:25,270
why I didn't trade you

638
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:27,240
for two bags of sweet potatoes

639
00:33:27,590 --> 00:33:29,350
or a few dozen tiles.

640
00:33:29,480 --> 00:33:30,790
I got mad the moment I heard that.

641
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:32,550
So I grabbed my shovel
and beat them up.

642
00:33:32,790 --> 00:33:34,030
If I sold my daughter like that,

643
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:35,590
what would that make me?

644
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:10,710
If you hate me,

645
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:13,710
just beat me however you want.

646
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:15,510
I won't dodge.

647
00:34:16,590 --> 00:34:17,960
Hit me all you want.

648
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:32,440
Thank you for telling me the truth.

649
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:34,280
You're right.

650
00:34:35,070 --> 00:34:36,110
Your abandoning me

651
00:34:36,550 --> 00:34:37,150
was actually

652
00:34:37,150 --> 00:34:38,400
a blessing for me.

653
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:40,960
Thank you for your wise decision.

654
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:43,630
Why do you put it like that?

655
00:34:44,590 --> 00:34:46,190
You might as well beat me up.

656
00:34:52,670 --> 00:34:54,190
I have two older sisters,

657
00:34:54,550 --> 00:34:54,880
right?

658
00:35:07,230 --> 00:35:08,000
Over there.

659
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,150
Look.

660
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,320
That's my eldest daughter.

661
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:22,710
Just take a quick look.

662
00:35:32,710 --> 00:35:33,760
You know,

663
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:35,800
I once had a little sister.

664
00:35:37,710 --> 00:35:39,000
If she were still with us today,

665
00:35:40,550 --> 00:35:41,800
she'd be about your age.

666
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,360
I've seen her.

667
00:35:52,590 --> 00:35:53,150
Mom?

668
00:35:54,590 --> 00:35:55,840
Mom, you okay?

669
00:35:59,030 --> 00:35:59,800
It's fine, Dad.

670
00:36:00,320 --> 00:36:01,150
Didn't hit Mom's feet.

671
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:02,710
We're all busy here.

672
00:36:03,030 --> 00:36:03,880
What's the matter?

673
00:36:04,150 --> 00:36:05,280
Nothing, Sanjin.

674
00:36:05,710 --> 00:36:06,840
Keep working.

675
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:07,880
We just came to check.

676
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,190
This is the one...

677
00:36:12,030 --> 00:36:13,000
The girl we left

678
00:36:13,480 --> 00:36:14,630
in town back then.

679
00:36:34,710 --> 00:36:36,320
You're my eldest sister.

680
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:43,800
Mom...

681
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:46,960
Mom? Mom!

682
00:36:48,000 --> 00:36:48,920
Calm down, Mom.

683
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:50,920
My sister's back!

684
00:36:51,670 --> 00:36:53,280
My sister's back!

685
00:36:58,190 --> 00:36:59,030
Calm down now.

686
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:02,440
Don't go near her! She's sick!

687
00:37:02,550 --> 00:37:03,400
She might hurt you!

688
00:37:04,480 --> 00:37:05,230
Mr. He?

689
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:06,710
Don't you know

690
00:37:06,710 --> 00:37:07,590
your daughter's sick?

691
00:37:09,030 --> 00:37:09,880
Bringing someone here,

692
00:37:10,150 --> 00:37:11,360
you should give us a heads-up.

693
00:37:11,630 --> 00:37:12,760
If her condition gets worse,

694
00:37:13,070 --> 00:37:14,110
how can we build the house?

695
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,030
Oh, well...

696
00:37:16,550 --> 00:37:17,400
You've seen her.

697
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:18,550
Let's go back.

698
00:37:21,630 --> 00:37:22,960
This is not the time...

699
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:37,510
You see...

700
00:37:38,070 --> 00:37:39,670
It's the busiest day for us.

701
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:41,150
I'm sorry.

702
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:42,590
Maybe...

703
00:37:43,150 --> 00:37:44,320
Come back next time.

704
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:56,760
How did she get sick?

705
00:37:57,190 --> 00:37:57,840
Stop asking.

706
00:37:58,320 --> 00:37:59,230
I need to ask.

707
00:38:02,670 --> 00:38:03,400
It's my fault.

708
00:38:04,440 --> 00:38:05,150
And yours, too.

709
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:07,110
Why is it my fault?

710
00:38:09,710 --> 00:38:12,190
Back when Xiaoqin was 19,

711
00:38:12,360 --> 00:38:13,710
she was engaged to a young man

712
00:38:13,710 --> 00:38:14,480
from the city.

713
00:38:14,590 --> 00:38:16,110
He wanted a dowry before moving

714
00:38:16,670 --> 00:38:17,630
to the countryside.

715
00:38:18,030 --> 00:38:19,150
But I was poor.

716
00:38:19,550 --> 00:38:20,880
I was reluctant to spend money.

717
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:22,800
But at that time, my wife

718
00:38:23,150 --> 00:38:24,630
went into premature labor.

719
00:38:25,150 --> 00:38:25,880
I was terrified.

720
00:38:26,230 --> 00:38:26,840
A premature labor

721
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:28,920
means it's probably a girl.

722
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:31,760
So I took some money and went

723
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:33,400
to the fortuneteller, trying

724
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:34,320
to change your fate.

725
00:38:35,150 --> 00:38:37,110
But he'd been arrested

726
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:38,440
for fraud

727
00:38:38,590 --> 00:38:40,030
and was being punished.

728
00:38:40,590 --> 00:38:42,230
We were afraid to get involved,

729
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:43,110
so we ran off.

730
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:44,320
But on the way,

731
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:45,590
you were born.

732
00:38:46,510 --> 00:38:48,150
If we hadn't met Ms. Fang,

733
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:50,030
the one who gave birth to you

734
00:38:50,510 --> 00:38:51,480
would have been...

735
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:53,710
My real mother...

736
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:55,510
Oh, don't say that!

737
00:38:56,480 --> 00:38:58,030
Ms. Fang raised you

738
00:38:58,030 --> 00:38:59,030
to this age.

739
00:38:59,070 --> 00:39:00,280
She must have spent

740
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:01,550
so much money and effort.

741
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,760
Do you know what this is called?

742
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:05,670
It's called fate!

743
00:39:06,070 --> 00:39:07,760
You can't change your fate.

744
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:09,590
Besides,

745
00:39:10,150 --> 00:39:11,110
Shenxian Peak

746
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:13,550
doesn't lack a woman like you.

747
00:39:16,670 --> 00:39:19,000
Your mother's name is He Hua.

748
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:20,960
On the way back after giving birth,

749
00:39:21,510 --> 00:39:22,760
the rain triggered her condition.

750
00:39:23,440 --> 00:39:24,710
She had a seizure.

751
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:29,070
Even with all the treatment,

752
00:39:29,150 --> 00:39:31,670
all the money spent,
and all the debts owed,

753
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,360
she didn't survive.

754
00:39:34,630 --> 00:39:35,550
Later,

755
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:37,480
that young man from the city

756
00:39:38,550 --> 00:39:40,030
saw my family's situation

757
00:39:40,670 --> 00:39:41,840
and broke the engagement.

758
00:39:43,150 --> 00:39:44,800
So my eldest sister
is sick because of that?

759
00:39:45,230 --> 00:39:46,150
They said

760
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:48,000
she was traumatized.

761
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:49,360
She couldn't stop

762
00:39:49,360 --> 00:39:50,550
yelling and crying

763
00:39:50,590 --> 00:39:51,440
when she saw us

764
00:39:51,440 --> 00:39:52,840
come back without you.

765
00:39:52,880 --> 00:39:54,510
There was simply no way
to calm her down.

766
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:57,480
She even sneaked into town

767
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:58,760
a couple of times,

768
00:39:59,190 --> 00:40:00,400
trying to find you,

769
00:40:01,030 --> 00:40:01,920
her youngest sister.

770
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:05,510
She went looking for me?

771
00:40:07,670 --> 00:40:08,670
It's been years.

772
00:40:09,320 --> 00:40:09,880
It's all

773
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:11,840
in the past now.

774
00:40:13,110 --> 00:40:14,510
Let's not talk about it.

775
00:40:31,710 --> 00:40:32,320
See?

776
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:34,070
They're butchering the pig.

777
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:35,480
Let's not go inside.

778
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:41,320
Hey!

779
00:40:43,110 --> 00:40:44,670
This is the girl

780
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:46,510
we left in town.

781
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,510
Ms. Fang's daughter.

782
00:40:51,670 --> 00:40:52,760
Oh, my sister?

783
00:40:54,030 --> 00:40:55,710
So you're my sister!

784
00:40:58,070 --> 00:40:59,550
I'm making pig blood tofu.

785
00:41:00,000 --> 00:41:01,630
My clothes are all stained.

786
00:41:01,630 --> 00:41:02,550
I can't hug you.

787
00:41:04,230 --> 00:41:04,880
Alright, then.

788
00:41:06,110 --> 00:41:07,440
You've seen the two you wanted to see.

789
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:09,320
I'll go back to dry the chili peppers.

790
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:10,630
Merchants are coming soon.

791
00:41:11,150 --> 00:41:11,840
Aren't you leaving?

792
00:41:15,070 --> 00:41:15,840
Then I'll go.

793
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:22,670
Zhao Kai!

794
00:41:22,710 --> 00:41:24,000
Come and take your dog away!

795
00:41:26,590 --> 00:41:27,590
Why are you barking?

796
00:41:27,840 --> 00:41:29,190
You're such an annoying dog!

797
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:30,550
Why do you yell at him?

798
00:41:30,550 --> 00:41:31,760
Just take him away.

799
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,230
It's okay, don't worry.

800
00:41:36,230 --> 00:41:37,360
That's my son,

801
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:38,510
your nephew.

802
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:40,480
He's in junior high now.

803
00:41:41,480 --> 00:41:42,510
Son, who is it?

804
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:43,510
I don't know.

805
00:41:43,840 --> 00:41:44,440
A woman.

806
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:46,230
Looks like she's from the city.

807
00:41:46,510 --> 00:41:47,150
Empty-handed.

808
00:41:47,630 --> 00:41:48,280
Empty-handed?

809
00:41:49,070 --> 00:41:49,880
From the city?

810
00:41:50,550 --> 00:41:51,360
Hey, keep playing!

811
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:53,480
Hurry up!

812
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:54,070
Xiaoju!

813
00:41:54,110 --> 00:41:55,030
Don't forget to cook!

814
00:41:55,230 --> 00:41:55,710
Okay!

815
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:59,000
We have guests here.

816
00:41:59,230 --> 00:42:00,280
I can't invite you

817
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:01,280
into the house.

818
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:02,800
Well, then...

819
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:04,360
You go ahead. I'll leave now.

820
00:42:05,070 --> 00:42:06,070
Hey, let's talk more.

821
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:07,360
Is your dad

822
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:08,590
still the county head?

823
00:42:09,320 --> 00:42:11,030
And has your mom,
the school principal,

824
00:42:11,030 --> 00:42:11,710
already retired?

825
00:42:15,400 --> 00:42:16,280
They're doing well.

826
00:42:17,550 --> 00:42:19,510
You... You have a niece, too.

827
00:42:20,150 --> 00:42:21,190
She's working

828
00:42:21,190 --> 00:42:22,400
in Yu County now.

829
00:42:22,630 --> 00:42:23,760
But jobs are hard to find.

830
00:42:23,760 --> 00:42:25,360
She's doing all kinds
of part‑time jobs.

831
00:42:25,510 --> 00:42:26,070
You see,

832
00:42:26,630 --> 00:42:27,440
could you please

833
00:42:27,440 --> 00:42:28,590
ask your dad and mom

834
00:42:28,590 --> 00:42:29,840
to help her

835
00:42:29,840 --> 00:42:31,320
find a stable job?

836
00:42:33,960 --> 00:42:34,550
I'm leaving.

837
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:37,150
Hey... Give me your address.

838
00:42:37,150 --> 00:42:38,360
Where should I find you?

839
00:42:39,440 --> 00:42:40,630
Guiyang Normal University,

840
00:42:41,150 --> 00:42:41,920
Chinese Department.

841
00:42:43,630 --> 00:42:44,760
Hey, your niece's name

842
00:42:44,800 --> 00:42:45,920
is Zhao Jun!

843
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:47,360
If she comes to you in the city,

844
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:48,630
be nice to her!

845
00:42:48,710 --> 00:42:49,840
You're the only upper-class

846
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:51,110
relative we have!

847
00:42:51,230 --> 00:42:53,000
Just give her a hand!
